  "title": "Cassandra Not Found",
  "description": "In this interactive mystery experience, you are the detective! Scour the Fringe site for clues. Solve puzzles. Take statements from suspects. Solve the mystery behind Cassandra's disappearance.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Sophia Cheoros and David Cheoros<br/><strong>Director</strong>: You!<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Ron Lamarre<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "Cassandra Not Found is a self-guided mystery. You start at a set location to get the story and instructions, then explore the Fringe site at your own pace. Along the way, you’ll find clues and solve puzzles to uncover what happened to Cassandra. At the end, return to the starting point to check your answers.",
